title: Action Hero Biju
subTitle: Biju Poulose leaves his teaching job to pursue his dream of serving in the police force. Posted as the sub-inspector in Cochin, he has to handle notorious criminals who indulge in unlawful activities.

title: Greetings
subTitle: Gopan falls in love with his neighbour, Sheethal. After learning that Sheetal has a plan to reunite a separated couple, he also pools in ideas, which leads to many unexpected events.

title: Sullu
subTitle: Jithu, a carefree boy, gets trapped in an abandoned house, forcing him to reflect on his life and appreciate what he once took for granted.

title: Oru Black and White Kudumbam
subTitle: Antony, a lorry driver, struggles with an inferiority complex stemming from his skin colour, leading him to create ongoing problems for his family.

title: Vakkalathu Narayanankutty
subTitle: Narayankutty wishes to be a lawyer but ends up being a clerk in a government office. However, when he sees the law being breached or misused, he does not hesitate to raise his voice against it.

title: Kammatti Paadam
subTitle: Krishnan returns home to Kammattippaadam after a call from his friend Ganga. Together, they face their dark past as old crimes resurface, putting their lives in danger.

title: Ittymaani: Made in China
subTitle: Ittymaani, who was raised in China, runs a business of counterfeit products in India. However, when he tries to help Annamma who is ignored by her sons, he lands in trouble because she falls ill.

title: Thanneermathan Dinangal
subTitle: Jaison, a teenager, has a crush on Keerthy, but she does not reciprocate his feelings. To make things worse, he gets in trouble with Ravi, the new teacher who is liked by everyone, especially Keerthy.

title: Pulimurugan
subTitle: A small village seeks help from a man with extraordinary force to protect them against man-eating tigers and the drug mafia.

title: Irupathiyonnam noottandu
subTitle: Appu, a restaurateur and surfer based in Goa, falls in love with Zaya. When she goes back home to Kerala, Appu takes it upon himself to find her and confess his feelings.

title: Irupathiyonnam noottandu
subTitle: Appu, a restaurateur and surfer based in Goa, falls in love with Zaya. When she goes back home to Kerala, Appu takes it upon himself to find her and confess his feelings.

title: Amrutham
subTitle: Gopi, a farmer, looks after his younger brother, Dinesh, a college student. Things take a turn when Gopi marries a Muslim girl.

title: C U Soon
subTitle: Jimmy gets ensnared in a web of uncertainty when his fiancee goes missing, leaving a suicide note. Later, Kevin assumes the mantle to unravel the enigma.

title: Mulla
subTitle: Lachi, whose father died mysteriously, falls in love with Mulla. Later, Mulla adopts an abandoned baby while Bharathan, who killed Lachi's father and the baby's parents, tries to separate them.

title: Casanova
subTitle: A group of masked fugitives kill the girlfriend of an international businessman, Casanovva. In order to avenge her death and capture the culprits, Casanovva sets up a fake television reality show.

title: Forensic
subTitle: When a psychotic murderer sets out on a killing spree, Samuel, a medico-legal advisor, uses his forensic skills to unravel the truth behind the heinous deeds.

title: Neymar
subTitle: Kunjava and his mate welcome a tail-wagging friend called Neymar, only to find their lives thrown into complete disarray.

title: Aadu 2
subTitle: Shaji Pappan and his team participate in a tug-of-war tournament to overcome their financial crisis. However, fate entangles them in a counterfeiting deal.

title: Bromance
subTitle: When Binto learns of his brother Shinto's disappearance, his search for Shinto leads him to collaborate with others, resulting in unforeseen turns, revelations, and memorable experiences.

title: Lalitham Sundaram
subTitle: When three siblings reunite with their families at their widowed father's home, old wounds resurface. Subsequently, their late mother's final wish forces them to confront the past and find closure.

title: Lalitham Sundaram
subTitle: When three siblings reunite with their families at their widowed father's home, old wounds resurface. Subsequently, their late mother's final wish forces them to confront the past and find closure.

title: Positive
subTitle: The passionate dream of becoming musicians comes to a standstill for a group of college students when their main singer falls in love.

title: Thelivu
subTitle: Gauri accidentally kills a wealthy businessman to stop him from molesting a little girl. When his minions chase after her and her husband, they must hide until the proof to exonerate them is found.

title: Ivar Vivahitharayal...?
subTitle: Vivek, the only son of two advocates, is an egoistic man. However, after his marriage to Kavya, a rift between the two crops up, thereby straining their relationship..

title: Chirikkum Thalika
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the best rib-tickling comedy scenes from various Malayalam movies featuring renowned actors and actresses.

title: Ohm Shanthi Oshaana
subTitle: Pooja Mathew, a spirited young girl, dreams about marrying only for love. Thus, she stops at nothing to impress Giri, who saved her once from a group of unruly men.

title: Adi Kapyare Koottamani
subTitle: Lakshmi, hoping to enter and exit the college hostel unnoticed, offers Bhanuprasad, a student, a sum of money. However, she ends up trapped in the building due to a series of chaotic events.

title: Neru
subTitle: Determined to seek justice, Sara Mohammed, a girl who is blind and a talented sculptor, joins hands with a disbarred lawyer as she goes up against her aggressor, the son of a business tycoon.

title: Brahmastra
subTitle: With Isha by his side, DJ Shiva rises to a crescendo of love and fortitude to embrace his role as the chosen protector of the universe's most powerful weapon.

title: Premalu
subTitle: Having been rejected once, Sachin, a young man, falls for Reenu, a girl he meets during a wedding, and sets out to win her over.

title: Bangalore Days
subTitle: Three cousins, Divya, Krishnan and Arjuna, share a close bond and decide to move to Bangalore to fulfil their childhood dreams. There, they face challenges that will change their lives forever.
